messages.content: 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
A plane crashed in Marshfield, on 17th in Lincoln, in houses.
A plane crashed? Oh my God. Where exactly?
Right in the backyard at 17th and Devine.
You said 17th and Devine?
Yes, the deck is on fire, and we need an ambulance and fire department.
Okay, slow down. A plane crash in Marshfield at 17th and Devine?
Yes, correct.
All right, hang on.
Oh my God, I don't know if there's...
Is everybody okay?
I don't know; I just saw it crash.
Is it 17th and Lincoln or 17th and Devine?
They said Devine, but I’m not sure.
Is the house hit or just the deck?
The deck is on fire, not the house.
Can I get your name?
My name is Rebecca McDowell.
And your phone number?
We've got an ambulance and fire department on the way. Stay safe, okay?
